{"000-section": {"000-title": "Skill Development Training \u2013 AP Mukhyamantri Yuvanestham / Nirudyoga Bruthi Scheme"}, "001-section": {"000-title": "AP govt. to start Skill Development Training Programme (Youth Special Training Program) for unemployed youth registered in AP Nirudyoga Bruthi / Mukhyamantri Yuvanestham Scheme, firstly apply online at yuvanestham.ap.gov.in to avail training from 10 December 2018 at 555 centers across the state"}, "002-section": {"000-title": "Skill Development Training Programme \u2013 AP Mukhyamantri Yuvanestham Scheme", "001-normal": "AP govt. has launched Mukhyamantri Yuvanestham Scheme on 14 September 2018 to provide monthly pension of Rs. 2,000 to unemployed youth in the state. Now the state govt. has decided that it will start Skill Development Training Programme (Youth Special Training Program) to provide employment to such jobless candidates.", "002-normal": "This skill development training program is applicable for all the eligible youth between 22 to 35 years of age. To create employment opportunities under [AP Nirudyoga Bruthi Scheme](https://sarkariyojana.com/ap-nirudyoga-bruthi-scheme-online-registration-unemployment-allowance/), govt. will take up a special training programme from 10 December 2018. This Skill Development training programme will be given in 555 centers across the state.", "003-normal": "The state govt. is going to spend Rs 24 crore. To avail this training, candidates must fill the [Mukhyamantri Yuvanestham Scheme online application form](https://sarkariyojana.com/ap-mukhyamantri-yuvanestham-scheme-online-registration/) through the official website.", "004-normal": "All the candidates enrolled in this [AP Mukhyamantri Yuva Nestam Scheme](https://sarkariyojana.com/ap-mukhyamantri-yuva-nestam-unemployment-pension-scheme/) can get this special skill development training programme. This training would be provided on the basis of the choice selected by the unemployed person."}, "003-section": {"000-title": "References", "001-normal": "\u2014 AP Mukhyamantri Yuvanestham Scheme Online Registration \u2013 User Manual  \n \u2014 [Download Mukhyamantri Yuvanestham Mobile App](https://sarkariyojana.com/download-ap-mukhyamantri-yuvanestham-scheme-mobile-app-online/)  \n \u2014 For more details, visit the yuvanestham.ap.gov.inofficial website."}}